'''Babajide Saheed Awobona''' (yin jiji to Azan ṣinẹnẹtọ, Afinplọsun, Owhe 1985 tọn) e yin Aihundatọ [[Naijilia]] tọn de, aihun kantọ podọ aihunbasitọ de po.
E yin jiji bosọ Yin pinplọ whẹ to Awọnlin amọ ayimatẹn Ogun tọn mẹ wẹ e geze te. E mọ yindidi to whenue e yin Sam to aihun lọ sitcom Jenifa's Diary mẹ.
== Bẹjẹeji gbẹzan etọn tọn ==
Jide Awobona yin jiji to azan ṣiẹnẹtọ afinplọsun owhe 1985 tọn mẹ to ayimatẹn Awọnlin tọn, to togbo Naijilia tọn mẹ.
E yin tovi ayimatẹn Ogun tọn, to togbo Naijilia tọn mẹ. [2]
== Wepinplọ etọn== 
Jide Awobona yi wehọmẹ dokọtọn etọn to Wesley Memorial Primary School to Awọnlin. E yi wehọmẹ daho etọn to Amuwo Odofin Secondary School, enẹgodo e Yi gbedewema Bachelor of Arts degree to Mass Communications mẹ
sọn wehọmẹ alavọtọn tọn Olabisi Onabanjo tọn to Ogun State.
== Azọn etọn== 
Jide Awobona bẹ azọn aihundida tọn etọn jẹeji to 2002, owhe dopolọ he mẹ e bẹ
azọnplọmẹ aihundida tọn jẹeji te hẹ Jovies Perfection Press mẹ.































